	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings Arjaizen Izrhume,<br><br>It seems you have been unwise enough to side with that weak High Elf Icewind Novastorm, and his pathetic plots against the rulership of Pusbag and Ourself.  <br>/ooc on<br>heh, it seems a lot of people are participatin now, interesting story is developing, so please keep posting, i need more victims<br>/ooc off<br>We warn you not to mettle in affairs beyond your scope of comprehension, and demand you withdraw any support you might have offered Our Elven cattle, upon pain of torture.  /cackle  Death is, afterall, a bit dull.<br>&nbsp;<br>Usula Wurmbane-Infection<br>Iksar Necromancer<br>Empress of Fear</td></tr>
